#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.poisson"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a Poisson distribution."
msgstr "从泊松分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson:3 of
msgid ""
"The Poisson distribution is the limit of the binomial distribution for "
"large N."
msgstr "泊松分布是二项分布在大 N 时的极限。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson:6 of
msgid ""
"Expectation of interval, should be >= 0. A sequence of expectation "
"intervals must be broadcastable over the requested size."
msgstr "区间的期望值，应大于等于 0。期望值序列必须能在请求的形状上广播。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson:9 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``lam`` is a scalar. Otherwise, ``mt.array(lam).size`` "
"samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定形状如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本。如果"
" size 为 ``None``（默认值），当 ``lam`` 为标量时返回单个值。否则抽取 ``mt"
".array(lam).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson:14 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson:16 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则将张量分配在 GPU 上，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson:18 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson:21 of
msgid "**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized Poisson distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的泊松分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson:25 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson:26 of
msgid "The Poisson distribution"
msgstr "泊松分布"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson:28 of
msgid ""
"f(k; \\lambda)=\\frac{\\lambda^k e^{-\\lambda}}{k!}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson:30 of
msgid ""
"For events with an expected separation :math:`\\lambda` the Poisson "
"distribution :math:`f(k; \\lambda)` describes the probability of "
":math:`k` events occurring within the observed interval :math:`\\lambda`."
msgstr ""
"对于期望间隔为 :math:`\\lambda` 的事件，泊松分布 :math:`f(k; \\lambda)` "
"描述了在观测间隔 :math:`\\lambda` 内发生 :math:`k` 个事件的概率。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson:35 of
msgid ""
"Because the output is limited to the range of the C long type, a "
"ValueError is raised when `lam` is within 10 sigma of the maximum "
"representable value."
msgstr ""
"由于输出受限于 C 语言 long 类型的范围，当 `lam` 接近其最大可表示值的 10 "
"个标准差以内时，将引发 ValueError。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson:40 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson:41 of
msgid ""
"Weisstein, Eric W. \"Poisson Distribution.\" From MathWorld--A Wolfram "
"Web Resource. http://mathworld.wolfram.com/PoissonDistribution.html"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson:44 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Poisson distribution\", "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poisson_distribution"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.poisson.poisson:48 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

